title: Protesters at New Orleans City Hall, airport rally against Trump's travel ban
text: At least a hundred protesters gathered at Duncan Plaza across from New Orleans City Hall Sunday (Jan. 29) afternoon, joining others nationwide who are voicing opposition to President Donald Trump's executive order
